    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  nulliparous

          -  &gt;/= 18 years of age

          -  not allergic to medications used for labor analgesia

          -  no contraindications to labor analgesia

          -  ASA I-II

          -  EGA &gt;/= 37 weeks

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  under age 18

          -  Spanish speaking only

          -  multiparous

          -  EGA &lt;37 weeks
